messages.message:
<!here> Thanks for your hard work towards the Aug 26 release. Our new release has a code freeze on Sept 23, so feel free to start planning around that once you’ve completed UAT and cherry picks.

We have a Release board here if you want to keep track of progress: https://instabase.atlassian.net/secure/RapidBoard.jspa?rapidView=57 And, you can now add Fix Version: “2019.09.23 - Release” to any issues you’re migrating to next release, or new ones you’re scoping.

Please make sure to do your part in keeping our engineering planning updated! (Work is still happening on the current release, but wanted to make sure to put this out there so you can start planning ahead as well)
